<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Harald Schwack – Unternehmensberatung</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script>
  (function(w,d,e,u,f,l,n){w[f]=w[f]||function(){(w[f].q=w[f].q||[]).push(arguments);};
  l=d.createElement(e);l.async=1;l.src=u;n=d.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];n.parentNode.insertBefore(l,n);})
  (window,document,'script','https://assets.mailerlite.com/js/universal.js','ml');
  ml('account', '1234567');
</script>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg:       #131313;
    --bg-mid:   #1a1a1a;
    --bg-card:  #1f1f1f;
    --text:     #f0ede8;
    --muted:    #7a7870;
    --teal-hi:  #00c4b4;
    --teal:     #009b8e;
    --teal-dk:  #006b60;
    --teal-lt:  #7fb3ae;
    --line:     #2c2c2c;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 4rem;
    background: rgba(19,19,19,0.94);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .nav-brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  .nav-name {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .nav-name span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .nav-link {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .nav-link:hover { color: var(--teal); border-color: var(--teal); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8rem 4rem 5rem;
    gap: 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 55% at 82% 38%, rgba(0,155,142,0.09) 0%, transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 35% 45% at 18% 72%, rgba(0,155,142,0.04) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 2rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--teal);
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5.5vw, 4.6rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--teal); }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.82;
    max-width: 40ch;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,155,142,0.3);
    padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover { border-color: var(--teal); }
  .hero-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding-left: 3rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .hero-logo-large {
    width: 110px;
    height: 110px;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0.92;
  }
  .hero-quote {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.72);
  }
  .hero-quote-attr {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .section-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--line); margin: 0 4rem; }

  /* ── SECTION LABEL ── */
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-top: 0.4rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }
  .section-label::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 1.2rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--teal);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── TWO-COL LAYOUT ── */
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ── INSIGHT ── */
  .insight { padding: 7rem 4rem; }
  .insight-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .insight-content h2 strong { font-weight: 600; color: var(--teal); }
  .insight-content p {
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.65);
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 62ch;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }
  .insight-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--line);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .insight-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: background 0.25s;
  }
  .insight-card:hover { background: #272727; }
  .insight-card-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--teal);
    opacity: 0.45;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .insight-card h3 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .insight-card p  { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ── LOGO SECTION ── */
  .logo-section {
    padding: 7rem 4rem;
    background: var(--bg-mid);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .logo-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 4rem; right: 4rem;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--teal), transparent);
  }
  .logo-display {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .logo-display img {
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  .logo-explanation {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .logo-letter {
    padding: 1.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    transition: border-color 0.25s;
  }
  .logo-letter:hover { border-color: var(--teal); }
  .logo-letter-mark {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .logo-letter h3 {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .logo-letter p {
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .logo-section-content p {
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.65);
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .logo-section-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* ── KI SECTION ── */
  .ki-section {
    padding: 7rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ki-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .ki-content p {
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.65);
    line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 62ch;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
  }
  .ki-example {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--teal);
    padding-left: 1.8rem;
  }
  .ki-example-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .ki-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.65rem; }
  .ki-step { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(240,237,232,0.65); }
  .ki-step-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--teal); min-width: 1.2rem; }
  .ki-step.ki-step-ai {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    padding-top: 0.8rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .ki-punchline {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.8);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── LEISTUNGEN ── */
  .leistungen { padding: 7rem 4rem; background: var(--bg-mid); }
  .leistung-item {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .leistung-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .leistung-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .leistung-item:hover .leistung-title { color: var(--teal); }
  .leistung-desc { font-size: 0.87rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; }
  .leistung-tag { font-size: 0.67rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); text-align: right; padding-top: 0.4rem; opacity: 0.55; }

  /* ── ÜBER ── */
  .ueber { padding: 7rem 4rem; }
  .ueber-content p { color: rgba(240,237,232,0.65); line-height: 1.85; max-width: 60ch; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-size: 0.97rem; }
  .ueber-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .ueber-tag {
    font-size: 0.69rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid var(--line); color: var(--muted); padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 2px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .ueber-tag:hover { border-color: var(--teal); color: var(--teal); }

  /* ── KONTAKT / FORMULAR ── */
  .kontakt {
    padding: 7rem 4rem;
    background: var(--bg-mid);
    position: relative;
  }
  .kontakt::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 4rem; right: 4rem;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--teal), transparent);
  }
  .kontakt-intro h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .kontakt-intro p {
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.6);
    line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 55ch;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* MailerLite form overrides for dark theme */
  .ml-embedded {
    --ml-bg: var(--bg-card);
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    padding: 1.8rem 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .footer-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem; }
  .footer-logo { width: 20px; height: 20px; object-fit: contain; opacity: 0.35; }
  footer span { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  footer a { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--teal); }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .hero-eyebrow { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.1s both; }
  .hero-title   { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.25s both; }
  .hero-sub     { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.38s both; }
  .hero-cta     { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.5s both; }
  .hero-right   { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.4s both; }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.6rem; }
    .hero, .two-col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; padding: 5rem 1.6rem;
    }
    .insight, .logo-section, .ki-section, .leistungen, .ueber, .kontakt {
      padding: 5rem 1.6rem;
    }
    .hero { padding-top: 7rem; }
    .hero-right { padding-left: 0; border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding-top: 2rem; }
    .insight-cards, .logo-explanation { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .section-label { position: static; }
    .section-divider { margin: 0 1.6rem; }
    .leistung-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .leistung-tag { text-align: left; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding: 1.6rem; }
    .kontakt::before { left: 1.6rem; right: 1.6rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-brand">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Harald Schwack Logo" class="nav-logo">
    <div class="nav-name">
      Harald Schwack
      <span>Unternehmensberatung</span>
    </div>
  </a>
  <a href="#kontakt" class="nav-link">Kontakt</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div>
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Unternehmensberatung · Wien</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Klarheit ist<br>
      die eigentliche<br>
      <em>Arbeit.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Bevor Strategien greifen, Veränderungen gelingen oder KI liefert —
      muss klar sein, was eigentlich gewollt wird.
    </p>
    <a href="#insight" class="hero-cta">Mehr erfahren →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-right">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Harald Schwack" class="hero-logo-large">
    <p class="hero-quote">
      „Die Technologie ist bereit.<br>
      Die Frage ist, ob Sie es sind."
    </p>
    <span class="hero-quote-attr">Harald Schwack</span>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- INSIGHT -->
<section class="insight" id="insight">
  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="section-label">Das Problem</div>
    <div class="insight-content">
      <h2>
        Unternehmen scheitern selten an<br>
        <strong>fehlendem Wissen</strong> —<br>
        sondern an unklaren Zielen.
      </h2>
      <p>
        Zielkonflikte, konkurrierende Prioritäten und schlecht definierte Anforderungen
        sind die eigentlichen Bremsklötze. Nicht Technologie. Nicht fehlende Ressourcen.
      </p>
      <p>
        Wenn Ziele unklar sind, führt jede Maßnahme in drei Richtungen gleichzeitig.
        Und jede neue Initiative — ob KI-Projekt, Reorganisation oder Strategieprozess —
        verstärkt das Rauschen, anstatt es zu reduzieren.
      </p>
      <div class="insight-cards">
        <div class="insight-card">
          <div class="insight-card-num">01</div>
          <h3>Zielklarheit herstellen</h3>
          <p>Was wollen wir wirklich? Und: stimmen alle darüber überein?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="insight-card">
          <div class="insight-card-num">02</div>
          <h3>Zielkonflikte sichtbar machen</h3>
          <p>Welche impliziten Werte konkurrieren — und blockieren die Umsetzung?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="insight-card">
          <div class="insight-card-num">03</div>
          <h3>Rollenklarheit schaffen</h3>
          <p>Wer entscheidet was? Wer ist wofür verantwortlich?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="insight-card">
          <div class="insight-card-num">04</div>
          <h3>Übergabe ermöglichen</h3>
          <p>Erst dann kann delegiert werden — an Menschen oder Maschinen.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- LOGO SECTION -->
<section class="logo-section">
  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="section-label">Das Zeichen</div>
    <div class="logo-section-content">
      <h2>Vier Felder.<br>Zwei Buchstaben.<br>Eine Haltung.</h2>
      <p>
        Das Markenzeichen ist kein dekoratives Element — es ist eine Aussage.
        Vier geometrische Felder, angeordnet in einem Rahmen. Auf den ersten Blick
        Quadrate, Kreis und ein D. Auf den zweiten: die Initialen H und S,
        einmal positiv, einmal invers gelesen.
      </p>
      <p>
        Genau das ist der Anspruch dieser Arbeit: Hinter der offensichtlichen Oberfläche
        die eigentliche Struktur sichtbar machen.
      </p>

      <div class="logo-explanation">
        <div class="logo-letter">
          <div class="logo-letter-mark">H</div>
          <h3>Harald Schwack</h3>
          <p>Oben links: ein Quadrat. Unten rechts: ein D. Zwischen den weißen Formen entsteht im Positiv der Buchstabe H — zwei Pfeiler, eine Verbindung.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="logo-letter">
          <div class="logo-letter-mark">S</div>
          <h3>Schwack</h3>
          <p>Oben rechts: ein Kreis, halb verborgen. Unten rechts: ein gerundetes D. Die weißen Formen lesen sich invers als S — die zweite Initiale, versteckt im Sichtbaren.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Harald Schwack Markenzeichen" style="width: 90px; height: 90px; object-fit: contain;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 38ch; line-height: 1.75;">
          Die vier Felder stehen auch für die vier Quadranten der Beratungsarbeit:
          Klarheit, Konflikt, Rolle und Übergabe.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- KI -->
<section class="ki-section">
  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="section-label">KI &amp; Klarheit</div>
    <div class="ki-content">
      <h2>KI kann vieles übernehmen —<br>wenn Sie vorher klar sind.</h2>
      <p>
        Die verbreitete Erwartung lautet: <em>„KI — löse mir Problem X."</em>
        Die Realität sieht anders aus: KI ist ein hervorragender Ausführer.
        Aber sie kann keine Fragestellungen definieren, die noch niemand durchgedacht hat.
      </p>
      <div class="ki-example">
        <div class="ki-example-label">Beispiel: Recruiting-Prozess</div>
        <div class="ki-steps">
          <div class="ki-step"><span class="ki-step-num">→</span> Wen suche ich eigentlich — und woran erkenne ich diese Person?</div>
          <div class="ki-step"><span class="ki-step-num">→</span> Welche Aufgaben oder Tests geben mir die relevanten Signale?</div>
